# -------------------------------------------------------
#  Appointly Solutions — Lead Scraper Configuration
# -------------------------------------------------------
#
# 1. Copy this file:
#        cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Replace the placeholder below with your real API key.
#
# HOW TO GET A GOOGLE PLACES API KEY
# -----------------------------------
# a) Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
# b) Create or select a project.
# c) Navigate to "APIs & Services" > "Library".
# d) Search for "Places API (New)" and click Enable.
#    (NOT the legacy "Places API" — you want the "(New)" version)
# e) Go to "APIs & Services" > "Credentials".
# f) Click "Create Credentials" > "API Key".
# g) (Recommended) Click "Edit API Key":
#    - Under "API restrictions", choose "Restrict key".
#    - Select "Places API (New)".
#    - Click Save.
# h) Copy the key below.
#
# BILLING NOTE
# ------------
# The Places API (New) Text Search is billed per request.
# As of 2024, the first $200/month of Google Maps Platform usage
# is free (≈ 8,000 Text Search calls). Enable billing alerts
# in the Google Cloud Console to avoid surprises.
# -------------------------------------------------------

GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your_google_places_api_key_here
